        <ArticleTitle>Staphylococcus aureus RNAIII and Its Regulon Link Quorum Sensing, Stress Responses, Metabolic Adaptation, and Regulation of Virulence Gene Expression.</ArticleTitle>
        <Pagination>
          <StartPage>299</StartPage>
          <EndPage>316</EndPage>
